{
  "stem": "1736.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 300.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had gone on similar trips, similar journeys previously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was March, '41.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were there for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure whether it's three weeks, four weeks, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at that point, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were told that Hitler's marched into or is marching into Yugoslavia and that we had to get out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] picked-- these are our youth leaders-- picked us up off the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I don't know how we're going for tape, but I mean--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so quick, you have to get to the railway station, get the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to move on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole group has to move on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was on my way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to Vitus, I can't go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why can't you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I had a watch that I had given to-- it was stupidity, but it was still a very big sentimental value.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a gift from my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had given it to repair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, I've got to get that first before I go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went the other way, the opposite way, whatever time it took.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went and got that watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we came back, we found that the train had actually left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Luckily for us, there was another train left, which is a goods train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was just about to go, so we jumped onto the back of that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went out with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, who knows?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was going out, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so but as it happened, further down the way, it caught up with the other one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were reunited with-- with that train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went from there to Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We arrived there in April.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
